      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WARREN'S LEDGER (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at Ballarat in a handy 21.70 beating Paw Jasta. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Great chance again. BLUE LABUBU (5) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and six minors from 15 tries. Placed last time (24.51) at Sale in a Grade 5, finishing third and beaten 4.5 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. GO GO EVIE (1) has missed the frame at her last couple but placed three back at The Meadows and she does perform well here. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. SHARAPOVA STAR (3) recorded a 0.8 lengths win (30.07) in a Free For All last time at The Meadows. Has already won four times from this draw.",
